<span class="hl_good"><span class="hl_keyword">lemma</span> secret_k_enb [heuristic={secret_k_enb}]:<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;all-traces<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class="hl_operator">∀ </span>q r #i #j<span class="hl_operator">.</span><br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="hl_operator">(</span><span class="hl_operator">(</span>Secret( &lt;&#39;K_eNB&#39;, r&gt; ) <span class="hl_operator">@</span> #i<span class="hl_operator">)</span> <span class="hl_operator">∧</span><br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="hl_operator">(</span>KeyDerived( &lt;&#39;K_eNB&#39;, r&gt;, q ) <span class="hl_operator">@</span> #j<span class="hl_operator">)</span><span class="hl_operator">)</span> <span class="hl_operator">⇒</span><br/>
